# Unity
*.cs diff=csharp text
*.meta text
*.asmdef text
*.unity binary
*.prefab binary
*.asset binary

# Native plugin binaries — never apply line-ending conversion
*.dll binary
*.dylib binary
*.so binary
*.bundle binary
Runtime/Plugins/macOS/**/* binary
Runtime/Plugins/Windows/**/*.dll binary

# Images
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.tga binary
*.psd binary
*.exr binary

# Misc
*.json text
*.md text
*.sh text eol=lf
